mp      I_cilp^%@Alias[D_sLD]\map.exe|mo^else^M_tinlp^endiff^set LIP=

: Who Am I

wai     I_cayli then^I_cipp %@Alias[D_sLD]\whoami.exe |mo^else^M_yanli^endiff

